  "detailed_description": "No Sleep for Sole is a surreal survival horror game about mental illness and abuse. You play as a young boy named Sole who stays awake at night to protect himself from the monsters he sees around his home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/145150d5d2031892d5632a0f881b84b0.poster.avif?t=1717189226\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/145150d5d2031892d5632a0f881b84b0.webm?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/145150d5d2031892d5632a0f881b84b0.mp4?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A detailed, disturbing story about abuse and its consequences.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An hour and a half of content with multiple endings.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tense survival gameplay that revolves around efficient use of resources.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Side-view sections that depict Sole's days.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Secrets and delusions.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/2baf98e03aeffb3fe3070dcd150e3cb5.poster.avif?t=1717189226\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/2baf98e03aeffb3fe3070dcd150e3cb5.webm?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/2baf98e03aeffb3fe3070dcd150e3cb5.mp4?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/280e9faf21d6455b6e40892ef5f85a16.poster.avif?t=1717189226\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/280e9faf21d6455b6e40892ef5f85a16.webm?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687000/extras/280e9faf21d6455b6e40892ef5f85a16.mp4?t=1717189226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
